{"tid":1649497,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"警察臥底都唔割","createTime":"2019-10-12T16:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T16:46:13.000Z","uid":37796,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e565e744805bc1cb20cfd89d34043e30d92eea","tid":1649497,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"個人原則：核彈都唔割<br />\n無論係咩人，警察臥底都好，都唔割蓆，只要係對準政權，放核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n政權範圍：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/DK8M3j9.jpg\" /><br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\ni :  <code>\n對準政權？這是錯誤的。\n你只對準政權，服從政權的人知道沒被對準，責任又可以推給政權，自然狐假虎威，為所欲為，因為被報復的對象不是他。\n應該對準服從的人，特別是他們的弱點。</code><br />\nCheng Lap<br />\nii :  <blockquote>他知道沒可能拿到六百萬人的民心的. 所以他的做法, 就是佔據各個香港運作的重要點, 政府與公務機構, 警察, 這些當然是不用說的. 但他最重要的是有方法控制各民間企業. </blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157470884672357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10157470884672357&d=NX17wA0xajt0Xz52GN5L9r500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=a789977f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10157470884672357</a><br />\n<br />\n不要說「臥底做既！」<br />\n試著說「多謝警察幫手！香港有希望！」<br />\n講得多，黑警都有機會變白"},{"pid":"c9204c824e7c40e436c0a16672ed77c5429feacc","tid":1649497,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d0ba08c7cce5b9fbc8486a5f35a95058c2f25b5","tid":1649497,"uid":91432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T16:30:49.000Z","msg":"收啦<br />\n明係間諜嘅都唔割？<br />\n害撚死成個運動！"},{"pid":"d4dd0999fbb350e2e6d2d